headline: Kick Out the Cold this Winter Season with 100 Energy Saving Actions from Consumers Energy
summary: Michigan's frigid winter weather is here and with colder temperatures comes an increase in energy consumption. Whatever your cozy is – inside by the fireplace, under a blanket, or with a hot cup of coffee, Consumers Energy is here to help keep you warm!
